In our policy, we use the term "cookies" to refer to cookies and other similar technologies that fall within the scope of the European Union Data Protection Directive. We use different types of cookies for reasons such as increasing the efficiency you get from our website, maximizing the user experience, adapting our website according to your interests, offering you special products and services, and improving our products and services. By using our website you accept the use of cookies and the processing of related data. We would like to point out that the privacy of your personal data Sundus Elektronik Para ve Ödeme Kuruluşu A.Ş. of great importance to We keep our system and internet infrastructure security at the highest level in order to protect your personal information.

Cookies, in general terms, the website you enter; is a series of text files stored on your device through your internet browser. For example, some of the cookies used remember your language selection, you don't have to repeat such choices every time you log in to the site. In addition, the cookies used create a more convenient and faster visit experience for your individual needs.

Cookies are divided into two as temporary and permanent cookies according to their storage time in your browser. Our website uses temporary and permanent type cookies to distinguish you from other users and to make arrangements according to your interests and preferences. SundusPay Payment Agency A.Ş. In addition to cookies designed by us, cookies can also be used within the scope of services received from third parties. There are two types of cookies, Persistent Cookie and Temporary Cookie, according to their duration.

The term session cookies is also used for temporary cookies. These cookies are created while you visit our website and are deleted after your browser is closed. The main purpose of our use of temporary cookies is to ensure that our website functions properly during your visit. For example; ensuring that multi-page and online forms are properly filled.
They are created when you visit our website and remain until you delete them or they expire. We use these cookies to provide an individual experience that is compatible with your personal settings.
Thanks to the use of technical cookies, the functional use of the website is ensured, but pages and areas that do not work on the site are detected.

: In case the site visitor logs in using a password, the identity of the site user is determined on each page he visits on the site, thus preventing the user from logging in using a password on other pages he visits.

These are the types of cookies that are used to remember the preferences made by the user on different pages of the website.
These are the types of cookies that provide analytical results such as the number of visitors to the website, the detection of the pages viewed, the time interval of the visit to the site.
